Tokyo Optical Co Ltd is issuing a 40 mlndlr equity warrant eurobond due April 27, 1992 paying anindicated coupon of 2-1/4 pct and priced at par, lead managerDaiwa Europe Ltd said.    The issue is guaranteed by Mitsui Bank Ltd and final termswill be set on April 9. The issue is available in denominationsof 5,000 dlrs and will be listed in Luxembourg. The sellingconcession is 1-1/2 pct while management and underwritingcombined pays 3/4 pct.    The warrants are exercisable from May 19, 1987 until April9, 1992. The payment date is April 27. REUTER&#3;